      readTime: "8 min read",
      intro: "GameFi (GAFI) is a blockchain gaming hub that combines a launchpad, game aggregator, marketplace, and yield farming into a single platform. The project aims to serve as a one-stop destination for blockchain gaming discovery, investment, and participation. GAFI is the utility token that powers the platform's launchpad tiers, staking, and governance.",
