    faqs: [{question:"What is GigaChad?",answer:"GigaChad (GIGA) is a Solana-based meme coin built around the iconic GigaChad internet meme. It functions as a community-driven speculative token."},{question:"Where can I buy GIGA?",answer:"GIGA is available on Solana DEXes like Jupiter and Raydium. Check centralized exchanges for additional listings."},{question:"Is GigaChad a good investment?",answer:"GIGA is a speculative meme coin driven by internet culture and community enthusiasm. It has no underlying utility or revenue model. This is not financial advice. Do your own research."}],
