    metadata: { title: "What Is Goatseus Maximus (GOAT)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about Goatseus Maximus (GOAT), the AI-promoted meme coin on Solana. Discover how it works, tokenomics, use cases, and how to buy GOAT." },
