      intro: "Goatseus Maximus (GOAT) is a Solana-based meme coin that gained fame as the first cryptocurrency to be significantly promoted by an AI agent. The token was boosted by the AI agent Truth Terminal, sparking a broader narrative around AI agents and meme coins that defined a new era in crypto culture.",
