      intro: "Gate Token (GT) is the native utility token of Gate.io, one of the oldest and largest cryptocurrency exchanges with a vast selection of trading pairs. GT provides trading fee discounts, Startup launchpad access, voting rights, and serves as the gas token for the GateChain blockchain. Regular burns from exchange profits reduce GT supply over time.",
