      intro: "Kamino Finance is a DeFi protocol on Solana that combines automated concentrated liquidity management, lending and borrowing, leveraged yield strategies, and a multiply product into a unified platform. Kamino has become one of the largest DeFi protocols on Solana by total value locked, offering users sophisticated yield strategies with a streamlined interface.",
