      intro: "KuCoin Token (KCS) is the native token of KuCoin, a global cryptocurrency exchange known for listing a wide variety of altcoins. KCS holders receive a daily dividend from exchange trading fees, trading fee discounts, and access to KuCoin's launchpad and other platform benefits. KCS also serves as the gas token for the KCC (KuCoin Community Chain).",
