    metadata: { title: "What Is Kujira (KUJI)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about Kujira (KUJI), the Cosmos-based DeFi ecosystem for sustainable yield. Discover how it works, tokenomics, use cases, and how to buy KUJI." },
