      categoryName: "Investing",
      categorySlug: "investing",
      readTime: "8 min read",
      intro: "MANA is the native cryptocurrency of Decentraland, a browser-based virtual reality platform where users can create, explore, and monetize content and applications. Built on Ethereum, Decentraland allows users to purchase virtual land as NFTs and build interactive experiences. MANA serves as the in-world currency for purchasing land, wearables, and services within the Decentraland metaverse.",
