    faqs: [{question:"What is Melania Meme?",answer:"Melania Meme (MELANIA) is a Solana-based meme coin themed around the Melania Trump brand. It launched alongside the wave of political meme coins and generated substantial trading activity."},{question:"Where can I buy MELANIA?",answer:"MELANIA is available on centralized exchanges and Solana DEXes like Jupiter and Raydium. Check current listings as availability may change."},{question:"Is Melania Meme a good investment?",answer:"MELANIA is a highly speculative meme coin with no fundamental utility. It is driven by hype, sentiment, and political culture. This is not financial advice. Do your own research."}],
