    metadata: { title: "What Is Neutron (NTRN)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about Neutron (NTRN), the CosmWasm smart contract platform secured by Cosmos Hub. Discover how it works, tokenomics, use cases, and how to buy NTRN." },
