    metadata: { title: "What Is 1inch (1INCH)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about 1inch (1INCH), the leading DEX aggregator that finds optimal swap routes. Discover 1INCH tokenomics and how to buy." },
