    metadata: { title: "What Is peaq (PEAQ)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about peaq (PEAQ), the Layer 1 blockchain for DePIN and machine economy. Discover how it works, tokenomics, use cases, and how to buy PEAQ." },
