    faqs: [{question:"What is Slerf?",answer:"Slerf is a Solana meme coin that became famous after its creator accidentally burned the presale LP tokens and airdrop allocation. The community embraced the mishap, turning it into a viral narrative."},{question:"Where can I buy SLERF?",answer:"SLERF is available on Solana DEXes like Jupiter and Raydium, and has been listed on select centralized exchanges."},{question:"Is Slerf a good investment?",answer:"SLERF is a meme coin driven by its unique origin story and community. It has no underlying utility. This is not financial advice. Do your own research."}],
