    faqs: [{question:"What is SPX6900?",answer:"SPX6900 is a meme coin that satirizes traditional stock market culture, particularly the S&P 500 index. It represents the crypto community's belief that digital assets will outperform traditional markets."},{question:"Where can I buy SPX?",answer:"SPX is available on Ethereum and Solana DEXes, and may be listed on select centralized exchanges. Check current listings for availability."},{question:"Is SPX6900 a good investment?",answer:"SPX6900 is a purely speculative meme coin with no fundamental utility. It is driven by community humor and market sentiment. This is not financial advice. Do your own research."}],
