    metadata: { title: "What Is Stader Labs (SD)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about Stader Labs (SD), the multi-chain liquid staking protocol. Discover how it works, tokenomics, use cases, and how to buy SD." },
