    metadata: { title: "What Is SushiSwap (SUSHI)? Price, Guide & How to Buy (2026) | degen0x", description: "Learn about SushiSwap (SUSHI), the community-driven multi-chain DEX. Discover SUSHI tokenomics, cross-chain features, and how to buy." },
